articles.title: Willie Mays dies at 93 - BBC.com
articles.description: Mays won the World Series with the San Francisco Giants in 1954.
articles.content:
Baseball legend Willie Mays, widely considered one of the best players in the sport's history, has died, according to the San Francisco Giants.
